            <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i> Industry Benchmark Analysis
            <small style="display: block; font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: none; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 2px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Requires Studio Access</small>
          </span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- PAGE WRAPPER / SECTIONS -->
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        
        <!-- SECTION 14: EXECUTIVE SUMMARY (Dedicated Page) -->
        <section id="executive-summary" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Executive Briefing</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">60-Second Boardroom Strategy Summary for Naa Anveshana</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-estimated"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Strategic Assessment</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: Cross-channel Synthesis&#10;Method: SWOT & Strategic Assessment&#10;Confidence: A&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="boardroom-grid">
            <div class="card-glass exec-card">
              <div class="exec-card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass-chart"></i> Top 5 Strategic Findings</div>
              <ol class="exec-list">
                <li><strong>High Brand Equity:</strong> Dominates the Telugu-language travel niche with 2.17M+ subscribers and 707M+ cumulative views across 1,230+ videos.</li>
                <li><strong>Culture and Lifestyle Outperformance:</strong> Culture-themed content represents 47% of top videos and yields the highest average views (5.31M views/video).</li>
                <li><strong>Proven Travel Footprint:</strong> Documented travel portfolio spanning 48 verified countries (85+ reported), establishing creator authority.</li>
                <li><strong>Extreme Virality on Anomalies:</strong> Vlogs highlighting severe economic anomalies (e.g. Zimbabwe hyperinflation) or high-tension regions average 5M+ views.</li>
                <li><strong>Revenue Concentration Risk:</strong> Over-reliance on standard AdSense, with minimal integration of sponsorships, affiliate networks, or merch.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass exec-card">
              <div class="exec-card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> Top 5 Critical Risks</div>
              <ol class="exec-list">
                <li><strong>Physical & Capital Burnout:</strong> Current model requires continuous, high-cost international travel, limiting long-term operational sustainability.</li>
                <li><strong>Algorithm Vulnerability:</strong> View traffic is highly dependent on YouTube home feed recommendations, exposing the channel to sudden algorithm shifts.</li>
                <li><strong>Rising Regional Competition:</strong> Younger Telugu travel creators are entering the market with faster editing paces and aggressive thumbnail hooks.</li>
                <li><strong>Unmonetized Community Trust:</strong> High brand affinity but zero structural audience monetization channels (memberships, merchandise, private tours).</li>
                <li><strong>Regional Language Ceiling:</strong> Operating strictly in Telugu limits target market size compared to national (Hindi) or global creators.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass exec-card">
              <div class="exec-card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Top 5 Growth Opportunities</div>
              <ol class="exec-list">
                <li><strong>Curated Subscriber Expeditions:</strong> Introduce premium, high-margin group tours (e.g., "Naa Anveshana Expeditions") partnering with local operators.</li>
                <li><strong>Affiliate Booking Integrations:</strong> Embed referral links for hotels, travel insurance, and flight search engines inside high-performing descriptions.</li>
                <li><strong>Hindi Dubbing Channel:</strong> Dub existing viral archives (e.g. Amazon, China) into Hindi to expand the target addressable market by 5x.</li>
                <li><strong>Tiered Membership Launch:</strong> Offer behind-the-scenes vlogs, raw travel updates, and monthly Q&As under a paid subscriber community.</li>
                <li><strong>Direct Brand Sponsorships:</strong> Sell flat-rate integrated sponsorships per travel series to premium travel, tech, or lifestyle brands.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass exec-card">
              <div class="exec-card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-award"></i> Top 5 Strategic Recommendations</div>
              <ol class="exec-list">
                <li><strong>Series-Based Content Structure:</strong> Transition to structured, seasonal travel blocks (e.g. "South America 30-Day Solo Tour") to build viewer retention.</li>
                <li><strong>Integrate Description Affiliate Links:</strong> Mandate standardized referral links in every description, capturing travel booking commissions.</li>
                <li><strong>Co-branded Group Tours:</strong> Launch two curated group tours annually, leveraging community trust to drive high-margin secondary revenue.</li>
                <li><strong>Implement CTR Optimization System:</strong> Update thumbnails to utilize high-contrast human facial cutouts, bright lighting, and currency text overlays.</li>
                <li><strong>Establish Dubbed Channel Pipeline:</strong> Select top 10 viral vlogs and launch a dubbed Hindi pilot channel to test national audience acquisition.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Embedded Boardroom Report for PDF Export -->
          <div style="display:none;">
            <div class="boardroom-report" id="boardroom-report-pdf">
              <div class="report-header">
                <span class="report-org">Naa Anveshana Creator Consulting OS</span>
                <span class="report-date" id="report-current-date">June 2026</span>
                <h1 class="report-title">EXECUTIVE BRIEFING REPORT</h1>
              </div>
              <div class="report-body" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; color:#333; padding: 20px; font-family: sans-serif;">
                <div>
                  <h3 style="color:#0f172a; border-bottom: 2px solid #00f0ff; padding-bottom: 5px;">Key Strategic Findings</h3>
                  <ul style="padding-left:15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <li><strong>High Brand Equity:</strong> 2.17M+ subscribers, 707M+ views across 1,230+ videos.</li>
                    <li><strong>Culture Dominance:</strong> Culture-themed vlogs lead views (averaging 5.31M).</li>
                    <li><strong>Virality Hooks:</strong> Economic anomalies and high-tension borders capture maximum traffic.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <h3 style="color:#0f172a; border-bottom: 2px solid #00f0ff; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top:20px;">Strategic Recommendations</h3>
                  <ul style="padding-left:15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <li><strong>Series Structure:</strong> Transition to structured travel seasons to lock in viewer retention.</li>
                    <li><strong>Affiliate Funnel:</strong> Mandate travel booking affiliate links in descriptions.</li>
                    <li><strong>Hindi Dubbing:</strong> Test dubbing top viral archives to target national demographic.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 style="color:#0f172a; border-bottom: 2px solid #00f0ff; padding-bottom: 5px;">Critical Risks</h3>
                  <ul style="padding-left:15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <li><strong>Operational Burnout:</strong> Physical and capital exhaustion from non-stop travel.</li>
                    <li><strong>Algorithm Dependency:</strong> View volatility due to platform homepage recommendations.</li>
                    <li><strong>Regional Cap:</strong> Regional language ceiling (Telugu) limits total audience reach.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <h3 style="color:#0f172a; border-bottom: 2px solid #00f0ff; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top:20px;">Growth Opportunities</h3>
                  <ul style="padding-left:15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <li><strong>Subscriber Tours:</strong> Curated high-ticket group expeditions for followers.</li>
                    <li><strong>Memberships:</strong> Paid community offering behind-the-scenes vlogs.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sponsorships:</strong> Direct luggage or booking portal integrations.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 1: HERO DASHBOARD -->
        <section id="hero-dashboard" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Hero Dashboard</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Real-time core performance indexes for Naa Anveshana channel</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-verified"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Verified Data</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Public Data&#10;Method: Public Channel Analysis&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="kpi-grid">
            <div class="card-glass kpi-card">
              <div class="kpi-card-header">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;">
                  <span>Total Subscribers</span>
                  <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Public Data&#10;Method: Public Channel Analysis&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" style="font-size: 0.65rem;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-value-container">
                <span class="kpi-value" id="kpi-subs" data-target="2175000">0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-footer">
                <span class="kpi-trend up"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-up"></i> +8.4%</span>
                <span class="kpi-trend-period">vs last 30d</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass kpi-card">
              <div class="kpi-card-header">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;">
                  <span>Total Channel Views</span>
                  <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Public Data&#10;Method: Public Channel Analysis&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" style="font-size: 0.65rem;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-value-container">
                <span class="kpi-value" id="kpi-views" data-target="707000000">0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-footer">
                <span class="kpi-trend up"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-up"></i> +12.3%</span>
                <span class="kpi-trend-period">vs last 30d</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass kpi-card">
              <div class="kpi-card-header">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;">
                  <span>Total Videos Uploaded</span>
                  <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Public Data&#10;Method: Public Channel Analysis&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" style="font-size: 0.65rem;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-clapperboard"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-value-container">
                <span class="kpi-value" id="kpi-videos" data-target="1230">0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-footer">
                <span class="kpi-trend up"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-up"></i> +14</span>
                <span class="kpi-trend-period">this month</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass kpi-card">
              <div class="kpi-card-header">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;">
                  <span>Countries Covered</span>
                  <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Video Playlists&#10;Method: Content Mapping Analysis&#10;Confidence: A&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" style="font-size: 0.65rem;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-value-container">
                <span class="kpi-value" id="kpi-countries" data-target="85">0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-footer">
                <span class="kpi-trend up"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-up"></i> 85+ Reported</span>
                <span class="kpi-trend-period">documented visits</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass kpi-card">
              <div class="kpi-card-header">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;">
                  <span>Channel Age</span>
                  <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Metadata&#10;Method: Audit of Channel Creation Date&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" style="font-size: 0.65rem;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-value-container">
                <span class="kpi-value" id="kpi-channel-age" style="font-size: 1.4rem;">7 Yrs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="kpi-footer">
                <span class="kpi-trend up"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-up"></i> Est. Aug 2019</span>
                <span class="kpi-trend-period">Active Since</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 2: EXECUTIVE COMMAND CENTER -->
        <section id="command-center" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Executive Command Center</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Key telemetry timelines of subscriber acquisition, video views, and publishing speeds</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-estimated"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i> Estimated Data</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: Social Blade & viewstats.com&#10;Method: Interpolated Trajectory Trailing Audit&#10;Confidence: A&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="command-grid">
            <div class="card-glass">
              <div class="chart-title">
                <span>Subscriber Growth Timeline</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Cumulative (Millions)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-container">
                <canvas id="chart-subscriber-growth"></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass">
              <div class="chart-title">
                <span>Monthly Channel Views</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Millions / Month</span>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-container">
                <canvas id="chart-monthly-views"></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass">
              <div class="chart-title">
                <span>Upload Frequency Index</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Videos / Quarter</span>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-container">
                <canvas id="chart-upload-frequency"></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass">
              <div class="chart-title">
                <span>Engagement Trend</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Avg Like-to-View Ratio %</span>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-container">
                <canvas id="chart-engagement-trend"></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 3: CHANNEL HEALTH SCORE -->
        <section id="health-score" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Channel Health Score</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Algorithmic metrics computing total channel health against industry standards</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-estimated"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i> Estimated Data</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: Modash & vidiq Benchmarks&#10;Method: Multi-vector Health Scoring&#10;Confidence: B&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="health-grid">
            <div class="card-glass gauge-card">
              <div class="gauge-svg-container">
                <svg class="gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 130 130">
                  <circle class="gauge-track" cx="65" cy="65" r="55"></circle>
                  <circle class="gauge-fill" cx="65" cy="65" r="55" id="gauge-overall-fill"></circle>
                </svg>
                <div class="gauge-score-value"><span id="gauge-overall-val">0</span><span class="gauge-score-pct">%</span></div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="gauge-title">Overall Score</h3>
              <p class="gauge-desc">Aggregated rating across all performance vectors</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass gauge-card gauge-engagement">
              <div class="gauge-svg-container">
                <svg class="gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 130 130">
                  <circle class="gauge-track" cx="65" cy="65" r="55"></circle>
                  <circle class="gauge-fill" cx="65" cy="65" r="55" id="gauge-engagement-fill"></circle>
                </svg>
                <div class="gauge-score-value"><span id="gauge-engagement-val">0</span><span class="gauge-score-pct">%</span></div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="gauge-title">Engagement Score</h3>
              <p class="gauge-desc">Likes, comments, shares vs active view velocities</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass gauge-card gauge-growth">
              <div class="gauge-svg-container">
                <svg class="gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 130 130">
                  <circle class="gauge-track" cx="65" cy="65" r="55"></circle>
                  <circle class="gauge-fill" cx="65" cy="65" r="55" id="gauge-growth-fill"></circle>
                </svg>
                <div class="gauge-score-value"><span id="gauge-growth-val">0</span><span class="gauge-score-pct">%</span></div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="gauge-title">Growth Score</h3>
              <p class="gauge-desc">Acquisition speed of new subscribers and baseline views</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass gauge-card gauge-consistency">
              <div class="gauge-svg-container">
                <svg class="gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 130 130">
                  <circle class="gauge-track" cx="65" cy="65" r="55"></circle>
                  <circle class="gauge-fill" cx="65" cy="65" r="55" id="gauge-consistency-fill"></circle>
                </svg>
                <div class="gauge-score-value"><span id="gauge-consistency-val">0</span><span class="gauge-score-pct">%</span></div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="gauge-title">Consistency Score</h3>
              <p class="gauge-desc">Upload frequencies, seasonal cycles, and format stability</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 4: CONTENT PERFORMANCE INTELLIGENCE -->
        <section id="content-performance" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Content Performance Intelligence</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Interactive catalog of top video releases. Search, filter, and sort video telemetry.</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-verified"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Verified Data</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: YouTube Popular Tab&#10;Method: Scraped Catalog Audit&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-glass">
            <div class="table-filters">
              <div class="filter-group">
                <input type="text" class="filter-input" id="table-search" placeholder="Search by video title...">
                <select class="filter-select" id="filter-category">
                  <option value="all">All Categories</option>
