                    <span class="breakdown-val" id="breakdown-affiliate">₹120,000</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="breakdown-row">
                    <span>Membership Fees (Exclusive content)</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-val" id="breakdown-members">₹140,000</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="breakdown-row">
                    <span>Curated Group Tour Packages</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-val" id="breakdown-packages">₹480,000</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 12: PREDICTIVE ANALYTICS -->
        <section id="predictive-analytics" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Predictive Analytics</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Machine learning forecasting timelines for Subscribers and Views under distinct velocity paths</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-forecast"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> Forecast Data</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: Scenario Projection Matrix&#10;Method: Growth Path Extrapolations&#10;Confidence: C&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-glass">
            <div class="predictive-layout">
              <div>
                <div class="scenario-selector">
                  <button class="scenario-btn active" id="btn-scenario-base">Base Scenario</button>
                  <button class="scenario-btn" id="btn-scenario-bull">Bull Scenario (+25%)</button>
                  <button class="scenario-btn" id="btn-scenario-bear">Bear Scenario (-20%)</button>
                </div>
                <div class="chart-container" style="height: 300px;">
                  <canvas id="chart-predictive-forecast"></canvas>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="forecast-cards">
                <h3 style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Target Targets (12 Month)</h3>
                
                <div class="forecast-item">
                  <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Forecasted Subscribers</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono);" id="forecast-target-subs">~2.5M</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="text-align: right;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-muted); display: block;">Confidence Bounds</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--font-mono);" id="confidence-subs">Illustrative only</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="forecast-item">
                  <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Forecasted Monthly Views</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono);" id="forecast-target-views">Verification unavailable</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="text-align: right;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-muted); display: block;">Confidence Bounds</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--font-mono);" id="confidence-views">Illustrative only</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="forecast-item">
                  <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Projected Annual Revenue</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-purple); font-family: var(--font-mono);" id="forecast-target-rev">Verification unavailable</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="text-align: right;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-muted); display: block;">Growth Scenario</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-cyan); font-weight: 700;" id="forecast-scenario-label">Illustrative Planning Scenario</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 13: STRATEGIC OPPORTUNITY MATRIX -->
        <section id="strategic-matrix" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Strategic Opportunity Matrix</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Quadrant mapping travel content concepts and untapped region optimizations against impact complexity</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-estimated"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i> Estimated Data</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: Creator Strategy Auditing&#10;Method: Impact-Effort Mapping&#10;Confidence: B&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-glass">
            <div class="matrix-layout">
              <div class="quadrant-container">
                <div class="matrix-axis-y"></div>
                <div class="matrix-axis-x"></div>
                
                <span class="axis-label label-high-impact">High Impact</span>
                <span class="axis-label label-low-impact">Low Impact</span>
                <span class="axis-label label-high-effort">High Effort</span>
                <span class="axis-label label-low-effort">Low Effort</span>
                
                <span class="quadrant-label ql-2">Quick Wins</span>
                <span class="quadrant-label ql-1">Major Projects</span>
                <span class="quadrant-label ql-3">Fill-ins</span>
                <span class="quadrant-label ql-4">Low Priority</span>

                <!-- Interactive nodes, positioned by JS/CSS percentages (left/top) -->
                <!-- Top-Left: Quick Wins (High Impact, Low Effort) -->
                <div class="matrix-node green" style="left: 15%; top: 20%;" title="Quick Win. Low setup barrier, immediate results.">Thumbnail Optimization</div>
                <div class="matrix-node green" style="left: 28%; top: 15%;" title="Quick Win. Captures immediate corporate brand spend.">Brand Partnerships</div>
                
                <!-- Top-Right: Major Projects (High Impact, High Effort) -->
                <div class="matrix-node purple" style="left: 70%; top: 25%;" title="Major Project. Expands viewership 5x.">Hindi Expansion</div>
                <div class="matrix-node purple" style="left: 82%; top: 18%;" title="Major Project. High capital, high reward travel epic.">South America Tour</div>
                
                <!-- Bottom-Left: Fill-ins (Low Impact, Low Effort) -->
                <div class="matrix-node yellow" style="left: 20%; top: 75%;" title="Fill-in. Low-production filler content.">Shorts Strategy</div>
                
                <!-- Bottom-Right: Low Priority (Low Impact, High Effort) -->
                <div class="matrix-node red" style="left: 75%; top: 80%;" title="Low Priority. High setup friction, low initial yields.">Membership Launch</div>
                <div class="matrix-node red" style="left: 85%; top: 68%;" title="Low Priority. High cost, niche interest.">Aviation Vlog Expansion</div>
              </div>

              <div class="untapped-listings">
                <div class="untapped-box">
                  <h3 class="untapped-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-flag-usa" style="color: var(--color-cyan); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Untapped Countries</h3>
                  <div class="untapped-tags">
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Japan</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Iceland</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">New Zealand</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Peru</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">South Korea</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="untapped-box">
                  <h3 class="untapped-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open" style="color: var(--color-purple); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Untapped Content Categories</h3>
                  <div class="untapped-tags">
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Expat Living Guides</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Solo Travel Gear Guides</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Visa Process Hacks</span>
                    <span class="untapped-tag">Hostel vs Resort Comparison</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 15: DATA METHODOLOGY (Dedicated Page) -->
        <section id="methodology" class="section-container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Data Methodology & Governance</h2>
              <span class="section-desc">Verification framework, data sources registry, and performance calculation formulas</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
              <span class="badge-tag badge-verified"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i> Model Specifications</span>
              <div class="gov-info-trigger" data-tooltip="Source: Platform Spec Registry&#10;Method: Mathematical Formula Documentation&#10;Confidence: A+&#10;Updated: June 2026">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="methodology-grid">
            <div class="card-glass">
              <h3 class="methodology-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i> Sourced Data Registries</h3>
              <p class="methodology-p">The platform aggregates data across four core intelligence vectors to build creator recommendations:</p>
              <ul class="methodology-list">
                <li><strong>Public YouTube Data:</strong> Scraped channel-level telemetry including total view count, subscriber size, video upload volume, and playlist listings.</li>
                <li><strong>Video Metadata:</strong> Relative upload dates, video category classification, language profiles, and semantic title hooks.</li>
                <li><strong>Social Blade & viewstats.com:</strong> Historical subscriber growth trajectories, weekly channel views velocity, and regional ranking indexes.</li>
                <li><strong>Industry Reports:</strong> Travel vlogging benchmarks, CPM/RPM estimates by regional market, and digital viewer density reports (RedSeer 2025).</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass">
              <h3 class="methodology-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-check"></i> Verification Framework</h3>
              <p class="methodology-p">We enforce a rigorous verification scale to maintain stakeholder credibility and prevent unverifiable claims:</p>
              <div class="framework-table-wrapper">
                <table class="framework-table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th>Tier</th>
                      <th>Rating</th>
                      <th>Data Type</th>
                      <th>Description</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td><span class="gov-meta-badge badge-verified">A+</span></td>
                      <td style="color: var(--color-green); font-weight:700;">Verified</td>
                      <td>Public YouTube API Data</td>
                      <td>Direct metrics from public channel endpoints (Subs, Total Views, Uploads).</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><span class="gov-meta-badge badge-verified" style="background:rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.05); color: #81c784; border-color:rgba(129, 199, 132, 0.2);">A</span></td>
                      <td style="color: #81c784; font-weight:700;">Derived</td>
                      <td>Calculated Telemetry</td>
                      <td>Mathematical outcomes of verified metrics (e.g. view-to-sub ratios, duration rates).</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><span class="gov-meta-badge badge-estimated">B</span></td>
                      <td style="color: #ffb300; font-weight:700;">Benchmark</td>
                      <td>Industry Averages</td>
                      <td>Aggregated travel niche benchmarks used in place of private channel metrics.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><span class="gov-meta-badge badge-forecast">C</span></td>
                      <td style="color: var(--color-cyan); font-weight:700;">Forecast</td>
                      <td>Statistical Projections</td>
                      <td>Linear or parametric extrapolations representing growth scenarios.</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-glass" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <h3 class="methodology-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-square-root-variable"></i> Core Performance Formula Registry</h3>
            <p class="methodology-p" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Below are the mathematical models implemented to calculate channel health, video virality, and engagement scores:</p>
            
            <div class="formula-flex-grid">
              <div class="formula-box">
                <div class="formula-name">1. Subscriber Growth Rate (GR)</div>
                <div class="formula-math">$$\text{Growth Rate (\%)} = \left[ \frac{\text{Current Subscribers} - \text{Baseline Subscribers}}{\text{Baseline Subscribers}} \right] \times 100$$</div>
                <div class="formula-desc">Computes subscriber acquisition velocity across quarterly and annual intervals to measure momentum.</div>
              </div>

              <div class="formula-box">
                <div class="formula-name">2. Viewer Engagement Rate (ER)</div>
                <div class="formula-math">$$\text{Engagement Rate (\%)} = \left[ \frac{\text{Total Video Likes} + \text{Total Video Comments}}{\text{Total Video Views}} \right] \times 100$$</div>
                <div class="formula-desc">Measures active audience participation. Used to calculate CPM pricing multipliers in sponsorship modeling.</div>
              </div>

              <div class="formula-box">
                <div class="formula-name">3. Content Performance Score (CPS)</div>
                <div class="formula-math">$$\text{CPS} = 0.70 \times \left( \frac{\text{Video Views}}{\text{Channel Baseline Avg Views}} \right) + 0.30 \times \left( \frac{\text{Video ER}}{\text{Channel Baseline Avg ER}} \right)$$</div>
                <div class="formula-desc">Custom weighted index identifying outliers. A score &gt; 1.0 indicates video outperformed typical baseline.</div>
              </div>

              <div class="formula-box">
                <div class="formula-name">4. Channel Health Score (CHS)</div>
                <div class="formula-math">$$\text{CHS} = 0.40 \times \text{Consistency} + 0.30 \times \text{Engagement} + 0.20 \times \text{Growth} + 0.10 \times \text{Coverage}$$</div>
                <div class="formula-desc">Aggregate rating out of 100 computing long-term creator sustainability against travel vlogging benchmarks.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <!-- Chart.js, JSVectorMap Core & Map Data CDN, jsPDF & html2canvas -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jsvectormap"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jsvectormap/dist/maps/world.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
  <!-- Main Script JS -->
  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
